Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么光芒?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从帝国首都那个方向发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对幸运圈?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由命运改变装置最后一次敔动\N所进行的命运改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会实现所有人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造出绝对的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是考验亚特兰提斯机械\N真正价值的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯就是因为那样才灭亡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈正在撒退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今主力部队遭到歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈已经没戏唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场胜利之后的事对我们巴斯兰才重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转向,朝北方去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在快去痛宰同盟的那群蠢猪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狄达勒斯军,狄达勒斯军发动偷袭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到战争可能会赢,竟然马上就来这招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要给他们好看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是西萨利欧王国成为盖亚盟主的好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击垮他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肤浅的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是少了我们,怎么可能会打赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着客气给我痛宰他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军来袭,敌军来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴斯兰军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盟约已经荡然无存了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在起内哄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士官长,是巴斯兰的浮游船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯多利亚的胆小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们给我轰掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降低高度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游石突然飞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往地面上逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人应该是寨巴哈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友军为什么要彼此攻击?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是人的想法使然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追杀残党根本就是小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的战役可还没结束,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够实现众人想法的,绝对幸运圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然让纷争更加扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们始终摆脱不了斗争的命运吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们渴望斗争吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然跟丢了迪兰度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡,孩子又得交给你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得要对我们的实验内容保密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扔下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死的话,我会很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的头发被他们剪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快点找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你快停下那部机器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们别再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运一旦启动,任谁也无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若人们真的要注定毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只有认命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的人型装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我找得好辛苦啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人,请您快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可以恢复成谢蕾娜…那个温柔的谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫贾久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个区区的兽人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把那个孩子带走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扔下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剑收回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人沉迷于战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要杀了他,就能断绝盖亚的祸根
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算杀了迪兰度也不会因此根除人们的愤恨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你岂能了解我的国家遭人毁灭的锥心之痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来当你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,你疯了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的罪就是我的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那全是因为她受到寨巴哈的妖术控制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量出招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一较高下吧,梵·法尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天空骑士亚连·歇萨尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会尽己所能迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢拉撒特与艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大跟国王打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一方倒下之前,看来是不会松手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士官长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵跟亚连为什么要对打?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全是他们的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的剑术真是进步神速
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真高兴,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能将人型装甲,操控得如此灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能使出如此精湛的剑技
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起了巴尔卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要击败他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个年轻人还真是j喻快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的愿望在绝对幸运圈实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再打下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全是因为多伦卡喀的机器在作怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多伦卡喀?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的命运持续不断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去盖亚也会跟亚特兰提斯一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我跟亚连做了了断之后就会去杀了多伦卡喀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要再打下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会结束这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去为王兄报仇,再将你给救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:11:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那种想法只会招致更多的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了保护你而战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没拜托你做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不该跟亚连动手的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只会担心亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么就是不明白我说的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明那么为你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满脑子明明就只想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么就是不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你肯相信他\N弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的意念有时足以撼动天地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是当意念与意念重叠在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒会导致巨大的隔阂产生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能够将其除去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就会跟着改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔阂…意念重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意念把梵给束缚住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的在为梵着想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心信任着他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草原的气息,梵的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢梵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没搞清楚的人原来是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认得我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都好想您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜…你终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再扔下你一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜…亚连的妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,我听到小瞳的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终时刻终于来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好比炼金术无法炼出黄金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运同样是无法操控的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放弃了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信命运并不是既定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒芜的心将引来龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨与恐惧会导致纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的龙…飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来带我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经启动的亚特兰提斯机械竟然会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人彼此吸引的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的意念…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:17:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌驾了背负着斗争命运之众人的意念吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,善变的人心所造就出来的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有可能化为永恒吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他应该对我有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是你想太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪,你好坏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去占卜看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看卓也是不是真的对幸子有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很擅长算命对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麻烦你帮忙算算恋爱运吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再碰占卜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄,我们终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我们的故乡,法尼利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你在这里守护着国家的未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得自己初次来到法尼利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是好久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你有什么打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠大家的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来建设盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄就是希望法尼利亚\N以及盖亚都不再依赖它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想见到那样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想跟你一起见到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好喜欢盖亚,好喜欢法尼利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:20:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓,如果你真想这么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我们随时都能见面不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要彼此的意念相通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带着吧,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算变成了老婆婆也绝对不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉学姊真让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟天野学长好相配喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是天生一对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过得很好喔


